content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Kamala Harris and Joe Biden killed the 13 fallen heroes of their botched Afghanistan withdrawal — and now, their allies in the Fake News are trying to make the story about me.They're truly disgusting, incompetent people.
